name: mosaic memory
description:
Isn't life, in the end,
only a mosaic memory?

-

A first NFT collab project of Jefta Mikola, Yosephine Salim and Karin Josephine. Karin is responsible for visualizing the mosaic fragments, while Jefta is here to enliven it with a few beats. Epin frames the thread between visuals and the beats through her narratives.
